            {"ref": "CD 2:14–3:4 (Damascus Document)", "type": "dss", "note": "The Qumran community's foundational sectarian document uses the Watchers as a paradigmatic warning: they fell because they 'walked in the stubbornness of their heart' — the same moral language applied to Israel's failures"}
